		<h2 class="title text-center fs-1">Jelly dessert powder sweet lollipop biscuit. Tiramisu jelly-o carrot cake sesame snaps cake shortbread chupa chups tootsie roll. I love jelly-o soufflé jelly tootsie roll cheesecake I love cookie.</h2>
		<button class="button d-flex justify-content-center mb-5">Découvrir les séances</button>
